License:        GPLv2
URL:            https://sourceforge.net/projects/e1000
Group:          System Environment/Kernel
Vendor:         VMware, Inc.
Distribution:   Photon

Source0:       https://sourceforge.net/projects/e1000/files/iavf%20stable/%{src_ver}/iavf-%{src_ver}.tar.gz

