- Adding generic template for iavf driver
* Thu Jan 04 2024 Roye Eshed <roye.eshed@broadcom.com> %{IAVF_VERSION}-1
- Package Intel driver iavf v%{IAVF_VERSION} for %{KERNEL_FLAVOUR}.
